<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= account.name %>'s Settings - Kids Finance Tracker</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>âš™ï¸ Account Settings</h1>
      <a href="/accounts/<%= account.id %>" class="back-link">â† Back to Account</a>
    </header>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="message error-message">
        âŒ <%= error %>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <% if (success) { %>
      <div class="message success-message">
        âœ… <%= success %>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="settings-container">
      <h2><%= account.name %>'s Account</h2>
      <p class="info-text">Configure the weekly interest rate for this account. Interest is automatically applied every Monday.</p>

      <div class="current-info">
        <p><strong>Current Balance:</strong> $<%= account.balance.toFixed(2) %></p>
        <p><strong>Current Interest Rate:</strong> <%= (account.interestRate * 100).toFixed(2) %>% weekly</p>
      </div>

      <div class="form-container">
        <h3>Update Interest Rate</h3>
        <form action="/accounts/<%= account.id %>/interest-rate" method="POST">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="rate">Weekly Interest Rate (%):</label>
            <input
              type="number"
              id="rate"
              name="rate"
              step="0.01"
              min="0"
              value="<%= (account.interestRate * 100).toFixed(2) %>"
              required
              placeholder="0.00"
            >
            <small class="form-help">Enter percentage (e.g., 5 for 5% weekly interest)</small>
          </div>
          <div class="form-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Update Interest Rate</button>
            <a href="/accounts/<%= account.id %>" class="btn btn-secondary">Cancel</a>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>ğŸ’¡ How Interest Works</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Interest is calculated as: <strong>Balance Ã— Interest Rate</strong></li>
          <li>Interest is applied automatically every Monday</li>
          <li>For example, with a balance of $100 and 5% rate, you'll earn $5 each Monday</li>
          <li>The more you save, the more interest you earn!</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
